6. Yuh-Min Chen and Jang-Jong Liu. Cost Effectiveness Design for Injection Molding. Robotics and 　Computer Integrated Manufacturing. 15 (1999). (NSC86-2212-E-006-112) (SCI/EI) 
7. Yuh-Min Chen, Chia-Ching Liao and Biren Prasad. 1998. A Systematic Approach of Virtual Enterprising 　through Knowledge Management Techniques. J. of Concurrent Engineering: Research and Applications, 　Vol.6, No. 3, September. pp. 225-244. (NSC87-2218-E-006-003) (SCI/EI) 
8. Yuh-Min Chen and Tean-Heng Tsao. 1998. Structured Methodology for Implementing Engineering Data 　Management. Robotics and Computer Integrated Manufacturing. 14 (1998), pp. 275-296. (NSC86-2212-　E006-034) (SCI/EI) 
9. Yuh-Min Chen. 1998. Integrating Geometry, Data and Knowledge: A Computer-Aided Concurrent 　Engineering Infrastructure. Journal of Integrated Computer-Aided Engineering. Vol. 5, No. 4, pp. 1-24. 　(NSC85-2212-E-006-101) (SCI/EI) 
10. Rong-Shean Lee, Yuh-Min Chen, Hsin-Yu Cheng, and Min-Dah Kuo. 1998. A Framework of a 　　Concurrent Process Planning System for Mold Manufacturing. J. of Computer Integrated Manufacturing 　Systems. Vol. 11, No. 3. Pp. 171-190 (NSC 85-2212-E-006-105) (Written by Yuh-Min Chen) (SCI/EI) 
11. Rong-Shean Lee, Yuh-Min Chen and Chang-Chou Lee. 1997. Development of a Concurrent Mold 　Design System: A Knowledge Based Approach. J. of Computer Integrated Manufacturing Systems. Vol. 　10, No. 4, pp.287-307. (NSC 85-2212-E-006-104) (Written by Yuh-Min Chen) (SCI/EI) 
12. Yuh-Min Chen. 1997. Development of a Computer-Aided Concurrent Net Shape Product and Process 　Development Environment. Robotics and Computer Integrated Manufacturing. Vol. 13, No. 4, pp. 337-　360. (NSC 85-2212-E-006-101) (SCI/EI) 
13. Yuh-Min Chen and Ching-Ling Wei. 1997. Computer-Aided Feature Based Design for Net Shape 　Manufacturing. Journal of Computer Integrated Manufacturing Systems. Vol. 10, No. 2, pp. 147-164. 　(NSC85-2212-E-006-104) (SCI/EI) 
